    <string name="about_heading">BUILT FOR THE\nLOVE OF THE SECTOR</string>
    <string name="about_summary">A focused, offline strategy game about calm decisions in crowded skies.</string>
    <string name="version_snapshot">VERSION 1.0 • DATA SNAPSHOT 2026–04–16</string>
    <string name="about_entertainment_title">Entertainment, not training</string>
    <string name="about_entertainment_body">This game uses simplified aircraft performance, separation, airspace and procedures. It must not be used for navigation, operational decisions or air traffic control training.</string>
    <string name="about_data_title">Airport &amp; data</string>
    <string name="about_data_body">Manchester is inspired by EGCC and adapted from a dated UK AIP snapshot. Harbour Approach is an original fictional crossing-runway sector. Both layouts and labels are deliberately simplified and incomplete.</string>
    <string name="about_privacy_title">Privacy</string>
    <string name="about_privacy_body">Progress and settings are stored locally and may transfer using Android device transfer. The game has no accounts, advertising, analytics or app network access.</string>
    <string name="about_disclaimer">Manchester Airport, NATS and airline names or marks are not affiliated with or endorsements of this game. Aircraft callsigns are fictional.</string>

